                </p>
              </div>
              <div className="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center gap-8 text-center">
                <div>
                  <div className="text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-400">847+</div>
                  <div className="text-xs text-neutral-500">Analyses This Week</div>
                </div>
